    C^{\text{KM}} = \left(\hat{S}^{\text{KM}}(t_0) - z_{1-\alpha / 2} \hat{\sigma} \hat{S}^{\text{KM}}(t_0), \hat{S}^{\text{KM}}(t_0) + z_{1-\alpha / 2} \hat{\sigma} \hat{S}^{\text{KM}}(t_0)\right)
