We know that \[\Exp{r_1} = n_1\Exp{1 - e^{-\lambda C_i}}{C_i}, \, \Exp{r_2} = n_2\Exp{1 - e^{-\lambda e^\beta C_i}}{C_i}, \textrm{and} \, \Exp{T_2} = n_2 \frac{1}{\lambda e^\beta} \Exp{1 - e^{-\lambda e^\beta C_i}}{C_i}\] Then the Fisher information is \[\begin{align}
